extendedInfo.description: This app is for those who want to practice English tenses and master it.App contains many questions with answers for you to study.The Practice Mode shows the answers if you get it wrong.The Test Mode will only show the score at the end, revealing the number of correct and wrong answers and the score percentage.if you don't know the answers to a question, you can share it via email to your friend or your teacher and get your answers. Isn't it amazing? More Free Apps button on the home screen will show you a list of other awesome free apps. More coming soon.. Keep in touch
